#. <section class="sutta" id="sn22.112"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.112:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.112:0.2"
msgid "11. Antavagga"
msgstr "11. Sides"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 112. Dutiyachandappahānasutta → dutiyachandarāgasuttaṃ (bj) | chandarāgi 2 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn22.112:0.3"
msgid "112. Dutiyachandappahānasutta"
msgstr "112. Giving Up Desire (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.162"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.112:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn22.112:1.2"
msgid ""
"“Rūpe, bhikkhave, yo chando yo rāgo yā nandī yā taṇhā ye upayupādānā cetaso "
"adhiṭṭhānābhinivesānusayā, te pajahatha."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, you should give up any desire, greed, relishing, and craving "
"for form; and any attraction, grasping, mental dedication, insistence, and "
"underlying tendencies."

msgctxt "sn22.112:1.3"
msgid "Evaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ pahīnaṃ bhavissati ucchinnamūlaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""
"Thus that form will be given up, cut off at the root, made like a palm "
"stump, obliterated, and unable to arise in the future."

msgctxt "sn22.112:1.4"
msgid "vedanāya …"
msgstr ""
"You should give up any desire, greed, relishing, and craving for feeling …"

msgctxt "sn22.112:1.5"
msgid "saññāya …"
msgstr "perception …"

msgctxt "sn22.112:1.6"
msgid "saṅkhāresu yo chando … pe …"
msgstr "choices …"

msgctxt "sn22.112:1.7"
msgid ""
"evaṃ te saṅkhārā pahīnā bhavissanti ucchinnamūlā tālāvatthukatā "
"anabhāvaṃkatā āyatiṃ anuppādadhammā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn22.112:1.8"
msgid ""
"Viññāṇe yo chando yo rāgo yā nandī yā taṇhā ye upayupādānā cetaso "
"adhiṭṭhānābhinivesānusayā, te pajahatha."
msgstr ""
"consciousness; and any attraction, grasping, mental dedication, insistence, "
"and underlying tendencies."

msgctxt "sn22.112:1.9"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ taṃ viññāṇaṃ pahīnaṃ bhavissati ucchinnamūlaṃ tālāvatthukataṃ "
"anabhāvaṃkataṃ āyatiṃ anuppādadhamman”ti."
msgstr ""
"Thus that consciousness will be given up, cut off at the root, made like a "
"palm stump, obliterated, and unable to arise in the future.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.112:1.10"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.112:1.11"
msgid "Antavaggo paṭhamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.112:2.1"
msgid "Anto dukkhañca sakkāyo,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn22.112:2.2"
msgid "pariññeyyā samaṇā duve;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn22.112:2.3"
msgid "Sotāpanno arahā ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn22.112:2.4"
msgid "duve ca chandappahānāti."
msgstr ""
